title: Previewing Top 10 Matchup Rivalry Game
description:
Jason Fitz, Greg McElroy, and Joey Galloway look ahead to the weekend and discuss all the factors going against Alabama and Tennessee. Plus, the crew tells us who they think needs to make a statement if they want to stay or make it in the Top 25. Also, the improbable success of interim coaches in Week 6... which coach has had the biggest impact on the field? And, what does Coach Robinson have to say regarding Deion Sanders?
